<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti sakavari
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṣa 9(6)9 sarvvaji
<lb n="3" break="no"/>t saṁvatsarada
<lb n="4"/>kārttika saddha pu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṇṇameyu sōma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>vāradandu śrī pṛ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>thvīvallabha mahā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>rājādhirāja para
<lb n="9" break="no"/>mēśvara parama bha
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṭṭārakaṁ cāḷukyābha
<lb n="11" break="no"/>raṇaṁ śrī madāhava
<lb n="12"/>malladēva pādapa
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṁkaja bhramara ni <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="14"/>saru sukhasaṁkathā
<lb n="15"/>vinōdadiṁ prithvīrājyaṁ
<lb n="16"/>geyuttire Aṟu
<lb n="17" break="no"/>varu seṭṭiya(rū) nū
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ṟa Irppadiṁ biruna
<lb n="19" break="no"/>ga(rar) piriyake
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ṟege ḷavaṇāyava
<lb n="21"/>nācandrārkka tāraṁba
<lb n="22" break="no"/>raṁ sale koṭṭaridaṁ ke
<lb n="23" break="no"/>ḍisidavaṁ prayāga
<lb n="24"/>ku bāraṇāsi yai
<lb n="25" break="no"/>du sāsira kavile <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="26"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> sira ka <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
</p>

